{"tid":1545172,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"係香港人既 入一入黎","createTime":"2019-09-05T23:25:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-05T23:59:36.000Z","uid":163990,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"a51739abd393a0863bb608f973b12fb34b4e551f","tid":1545172,"uid":163990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T23:25:46.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">無錯 的確係已經撤回逃犯條例［/red]</span></strong><br />\n[black]咁多位大足，唔知大家仲記唔記得點解要企出黎，就係因為呢個[red]政權</span>既壓迫[/black]<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">無錯 的確係撤回左！</span></div><br />\n<strong>但係仲記唔記得佢有講過 就算講左撤回 三個月後都可以重啟</strong><br />\n咁證明左啲咩野？一路以黎我地叫緊既口號 「林鄭 下台」係必要<br />\n  <div style=\"text-align: center;\">必須要推翻林鄭 如果唔係就只會一直活在恐懼之中</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><ins><strong>所以大家 九月八日 齊上齊落</strong></ins></div>"},{"pid":"b73bbacb6f2e5ffebff66a6a8b5562975563c03f","tid":1545172,"uid":123991,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T23:25:51.000Z","msg":"[行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/reLz9Yb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FreLz9Yb.jpg&h=bc5ea362&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VeJJ3id.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVeJJ3id.jpg&h=50bde3c1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5d3812e6d9d63112d6ef71968b81b8bceefd1b15","tid":1545172,"uid":163990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a51739abd393a0863bb608f973b12fb34b4e551f","tid":1545172,"uid":163990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T23:25:46.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">無錯 的確係已經撤回逃犯條例［/red]</span></strong><br />\n[black]咁多位大足，唔知大家仲記唔記得點解要企出黎，就係因為呢個[red]